---
import StarlightPage from '@astrojs/starlight/components/StarlightPage.astro';
---

<StarlightPage
  frontmatter={{
    title: 'Demo Time as a Service',
    description: 'Stop spending days building demos with Demo Time as a Service.',
    tableOfContents: false,
  }}
>
  <div class="service-page">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <header class="hero">
      <h2>Let's ship a flawless demo in days, not weeks.</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Demo Time as a Service</strong> turns your repo into a ready-to-present demo for VS Code.
      </p>
      <p>No broken commands. No scramble. Just a confident delivery your audience will trust.</p>
    </header>

    {/* Problem Section */}
    <section>
      <h3>The challenge: why demos take so much time</h3>
      <p>
        I've talked to hundreds of presenters, and they all describe the same friction points. I
        know because I've felt them myself as a speaker and MVP.
      </p>

      <p>
        It's not just frustration; it's lost time. <strong
          >A high-quality technical demo can easily take a day or more to build.</strong
        > That's engineering time you can't get back.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Close faster:</strong> A crisp, working demo removes doubt for buyers and stakeholders.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Save time:</strong> I'll build the flow so your team stays focused on product work.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Stress-proof:</strong> Every step is scripted, tested, and ready for live delivery.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    {/* Offer Section */}
    <section>
      <h3>What I'll build for you</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>One ready-to-run Demo Time script (up to ~15 minutes).</li>
        <li>Storyline crafted from your git commits—no guesswork.</li>
        <li>2 revision rounds and a 30-minute onboarding.</li>
        <li>Standard turnaround: 5-7 business days.</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Price: € 500 per demo (early bird for the first 10 teams).</strong></p>
      <p>Need live help instead? Coaching is available at € 200/hour.</p>
    </section>

    {/* How It Works Section */}
    <section>
      <h3>How it works</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Share your repo</strong> and the story you need to tell.</li>
        <li><strong>I script and test</strong> every step inside Demo Time.</li>
        <li><strong>You present</strong> with a reliable, polished demo.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    {/* Fit Section */}
    <section>
      <h3>Is this for you?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Sales engineers and solutions teams who need a clean, working demo next week.</li>
        <li>DevRel and product teams showing new features with zero risk of breaking on stage.</li>
        <li>Training orgs that want reusable, consistent demos for courses and workshops.</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Works best for code-based demos you control in VS Code.</strong></p>
    </section>

    {/* Quick FAQ Section */}
    <section>
      <h3>Quick answers</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Format:</strong> Delivered as a Demo Time YAML script, ready to run.</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Turnaround:</strong> 5-7 business days (rush &lt;3 days available at +€ 250).
        </li>
        <li><strong>Not sure your repo is clean?</strong> We’ll guide you or add coaching time.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    {/* CTA Section */}
    <section id="get-started">
      <h2>Lock in your slot</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>€ 500 per demo, limited early-bird capacity.</strong> Tell us about your demo and we’ll
        start this week.
      </p>

      <form
        id="interestForm"
        class="interest-form"
        action="https://formbold.com/s/obkNp"
        method="POST"
      >
        <input type="hidden" name="apiKey" value="sf_2g9h855e668na16n94fl0lh4" />
        <input type="hidden" name="subject" value="Demo Time Service Interest" />
        <input type="hidden" name="replyTo" value="@replyEmail" />
        <input type="text" name="honeypot" style="display: none" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Full Name</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="John Doe" required />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email Address</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="john@example.com" required />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="organization">Organization/Company</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <input
              type="text"
              id="organization"
              name="organization"
              placeholder="Demo Time, etc."
              required
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="role">Your Role</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <select id="role" name="role" required>
              <option value="">Select your role...</option>
              <option value="training-manager">Training Manager</option>
              <option value="devrel">Developer Relations</option>
              <option value="content-creator">Content Creator</option>
              <option value="conference-organizer">Conference Organizer</option>
              <option value="other">Other</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Which services are you interested in?</label>
          <div class="checkbox-group">
            <label class="checkbox-label">
              <input type="checkbox" name="$services" value="creation" checked />
              Demo creation service (€ 500)
            </label>
            <label class="checkbox-label">
              <input type="checkbox" name="$services" value="coaching" />
              Expert coaching (€ 200/hour)
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="demoDescription"
            >What types of demos does your organization create? (1-2 sentences)</label
          >
          <div class="input-group">
            <textarea
              id="demoDescription"
              name="demoDescription"
              rows="2"
              placeholder="e.g., Hands-on labs for developer training, product feature demonstrations, conference workshops"
              required></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="frequency">How many demos does your team create per quarter?</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <select id="frequency" name="frequency" required>
              <option value="">Select quantity...</option>
              <option value="1-5">1-5 demos</option>
              <option value="6-10">6-10 demos</option>
              <option value="11-20">11-20 demos</option>
              <option value="20+">20+ demos</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="challenge">What's your biggest challenge with demo creation right now?</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <textarea
              id="challenge"
              name="challenge"
              rows="2"
              placeholder="e.g., Takes too long to create, demos break during live sessions, hard to maintain when product updates"
              required></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="willingness">Is € 500 per demo within your budget?</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <select id="willingness" name="willingness" required>
              <option value="">Select answer...</option>
              <option value="yes">Yes, this is reasonable</option>
              <option value="need-approval">Yes, but need approval</option>
              <option value="multiple">Yes, interested in ordering multiple demos</option>
              <option value="too-high">This seems too high</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Additional questions or comments (Optional)</label>
          <div class="input-group">
            <textarea
              id="message"
              name="message"
              rows="3"
              placeholder="Any questions or specific requirements?"></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="g-recaptcha" data-sitekey="6Lct-gkrAAAAANXSF_L-hUZUyP-pF4oWzyO0M4jL"></div>

        <script src="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js" is:inline></script>

        <button id="submitButton" type="submit" class="button primary full-width">
          Join the Waitlist
        </button>
      </form>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <p>
          <strong>Questions?</strong> Reach out at <a href="mailto:elio@struyfconsulting.be"
            >elio@struyfconsulting.be</a
          >
        </p>
        <p>Let's make demos less stressful and more impactful—together!</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</StarlightPage>

<style>
  :root {
    --sl-content-width: 50rem;
  }

  .service-page {
    max-width: 50rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .hero {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  /* Form */
  .interest-form {
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-gray-6);
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  input[type='text'],
  input[type='email'],
  textarea,
  select {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-4);
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-black);
    color: var(--sl-color-white);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  input:focus,
  textarea:focus,
  select:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--sl-color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--sl-color-accent-low);
  }

  select {
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .checkbox-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .checkbox-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: normal;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .checkbox-label input {
    margin: 0;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1rem;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .button.primary {
    background: rgb(255 212 59 / var(--tw-bg-opacity, 1)) !important;
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-text-accent);
    color: #000;
  }

  .button.primary:hover {
    color: #000;
    background-color: rgb(255 212 59 / 0.8) !important;
  }

  .button.full-width {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .contact-info {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-info a {
    color: var(--sl-color-accent-high);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-info a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .g-recaptcha {
    div,
    iframe {
      height: 78px !important;
    }
  }
</style>
